src:
Ny maktdemonstrasjon av Viking – knuste Lillestrøm
03 Nov 2019, 18:53 by Kjetil Flygind
Viking fortsatte der de slapp i cupfesten mot Ranheim da Lillestrøm fikk bank i serien. Men selve kampen var lite å rope hurra for.

VIKING-LILLESTRØM 3–0
text:
New power demonstration of Viking - crushed Lillestrøm
03 Nov 2019, 18:53 by Kjetil Flygind
Viking continued where they left off in the cup party against Ranheim when Lillestrøm got knocked out in the series. But the fight itself was little to shout for.

VIKING-LILLSTREAM 3–0
